{"tid":1032432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：預算案預留逾五億元翻新公廁","createTime":"2019-02-22T10:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T10:12:07.000Z","uid":81228,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f511891271812f967c1505cf52677eb2052a77f2","tid":1032432,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】財政預算案下周三發表，消息指預算案擬預留超過五億元翻新超過200個公廁，包括改善通風及提升衞生設施。<br />\n<br />\n在街上人有三急，但公廁很多時令人卻步，荃灣楊屋道街市的公廁，在外面已聞到異味，地面濕滑，牆邊沾有排泄物，廁板發黃，廁所淤塞，有些廁格還長期待修。葵芳這個公廁還暫停鹹水供應，無法沖廁，很多市民對公廁印象都甚差。<br />\n<br />\n有公廁五年多前用300多萬翻新過，情況如何清潔工最清楚。<br />\n<br />\n全港有近八百個公廁，消息指新一份預算案將預留超過五億元，在幾年內翻新超過二百個公廁，平均用250萬元翻新一個公廁，主要改善通風、更換老化設施、提升衞生設備等，不會優先考慮旅遊景點附近的公廁。<br />\n<br />\n食環署過往都有翻新公廁，過去三個年度翻新了34個公廁，部分是鄉郊的旱廁，最貴的翻新工程耗資達八百萬。<br />\n<br />\n香港廁所協會認為本港公廁老化落後，與大都會形象相違背，必須加快翻新公廁。協會還建議在公廁外牆加添壁畫，改善市民和遊客的觀感。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=338416&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338416%26hot%3D1&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=ef0c0fe2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338416%26hot%3D1&h=4ca9ec8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=338416&amp;hot=1</a>"},{"pid":"a070ef5c593aca495c421fd75be375564d8f51e9","tid":1032432,"uid":54884,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"呢項好有用"},{"pid":"98bf29090b3794eddaafaa71c8abdfd669298475","tid":1032432,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"強國人優先使用<br />\n<br />\n踩爆你屎塔<br />\n<br />\n偷你廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48446c911be037571f0448f7ef2ed74fc9f0b6e9","tid":1032432,"uid":76796,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"算好啦<br />\n好多公廁真係臭到鳩縮<br />\n一樣還一樣，住屋問題同150 一定要解決<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c118b60d1f5583ae4ece6973e0973903d93cc27","tid":1032432,"uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:19:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>團體倡仿新加坡建綠化廁</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190222/s00001/d107ada49878fc4f599e918e417b113a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2Fd107ada49878fc4f599e918e417b113a.jpg&h=bc0ecd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190222/s00001/d10529daebb674a3aa2662251b62db91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2Fd10529daebb674a3aa2662251b62db91.jpg&h=48e11d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190222/s00001/d1061665a9c6fdd9fec9cfedc0c74a2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2Fd1061665a9c6fdd9fec9cfedc0c74a2e.jpg&h=17bf7aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190222/s00001/d106f82a973ae70e40c27e484f9bf9a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2Fd106f82a973ae70e40c27e484f9bf9a5.jpg&h=ec7da4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新加坡一間公廁的地磚和牆身都佈滿裝飾，並擺有綠化植物，沒有積水，衛生良好。（香港廁所協會副主席熊志權提供）<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平早於2015年提出推行「廁所革命」，全國開展公廁改造升級計劃，4年後此「革命」要捲來香港。消息人士指，港府下周發表的財政預算案會預留逾5億元，翻新全港逾200個公廁，佔本港食環署轄下約800公廁的四分一，即平均每個公廁花費250萬元，以改善通風衛生和更換設備等。有團體促請港府藉此參考新加坡做法，加強維修、衛生、內籠設計和綠化公廁，提升市民的生活質素。<br />\n<br />\n一些街頭街尾的公廁，外圍仍會讓人嗅到陣陣臭味，走進去，廁所淤塞、地面濕滑骯髒、吹風機和燈管等壞掉，處處可見。繼去年財政預算案提出撥款20億元推行十年街市現代化計劃後，消息人士指，港府下周公布的預算案，亦決定會處理食環署轄下另一項重點設施：公共廁所；港府將預留逾5億元，翻新全港逾200個公廁，即預計平均花250萬元翻新一個。<br />\n<br />\n香港廁所協會副主席熊志權形容是好消息，認為應優先翻新人煙稠密地區如尖沙嘴和深水埗的公廁，長遠應逐步改善全數公廁的環境。熊指，雖然250萬元不足以完成重建或大型裝修一個公廁，但相信更換抽風系統、地磚和牆身，並加種植物等，亦已足夠。<br />\n<br />\n熊志權稱，剛到過新加坡考察，當地機場附近一個公廁，既備有良好通風系統，其地磚和牆身更佈滿裝飾，並有綠化植物，沒有積水和異味。他又指，當地的公廁設計會配合周遭環境，例如有公園的公廁會有大量綠化，看上去像小森林，營造舒適和輕鬆的環境。熊認為，港府可模仿當地的公廁設計，加強本港公廁的通風系統甚或增設冷氣，換成自動化沖廁和水龍頭並加種植物。<br />\n<br />\n「做好翻新之後的維修保養做得不好就很快損耗，多漂亮的廁所也無用。」熊志權指出，公廁翻新後，港府要投放更多恆常資源，因應公廁人流加密清潔次數，以馬上移走廁所淤塞物，改善公廁濕滑和臭味問題，做到乾淨無污漬為目標，好扭轉市民對公廁就是藏污納垢的印象，並提升市民的生活質素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190222/s00001/1550833923478/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E7%95%995%E5%84%84%E7%BF%BB%E6%96%B0%E9%80%BE200%E5%85%AC%E5%BB%81-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E5%80%A1%E4%BB%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%BB%BA%E7%B6%A0%E5%8C%96%E5%BB%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2F1550833923478%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E7%2595%25995%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25BB%2581-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2580%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25BB%2581&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=4964576b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2F1550833923478%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E7%2595%25995%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25BB%2581-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2580%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25BB%2581&h=57ad8e0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190222/s00001/1550833923478/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E7%95%995%E5%84%84%E7%BF%BB%E6%96%B0%E9%80%BE200%E5%85%AC%E5%BB%81-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E5%80%A1%E4%BB%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%BB%BA%E7%B6%A0%E5%8C%96%E5%BB%81</a>"},{"pid":"5d7d5f54b88d1e968d6baa55711667d34aae2ba8","tid":1032432,"uid":3874,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"啲廢老亂鳩咁痾 點翻新都一鳩樣嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626730650e882d5bcca4510a170cc4437e75d89a","tid":1032432,"uid":174013,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:32:09.000Z","msg":"250萬翻新一個公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又比人貪左幾多走"},{"pid":"9eb623858df6e1967d7e120992bb91b44fcb322b","tid":1032432,"uid":166766,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"5d7d5f54b88d1e968d6baa55711667d34aae2ba8","tid":1032432,"uid":3874,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"啲廢老亂鳩咁痾 點翻新都一鳩樣嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n就算大商場廁所開頭靚一靚 <br />\n耐少少俾強國客成日用好快變得又殘又臭<br />\n班老野痾尿唔瞄準  又亂吐痰<br />\n翻新到幾靚都好快打柴"},{"pid":"3fd77ad1bedeef878de1fb4e809e95f3df005b6c","tid":1032432,"uid":130695,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"對門用智能身分證解鎖 + 禁止 R字中国人使用"},{"pid":"8b95d55e2bf83b6fa6f96a6b97292d10c00a55f8","tid":1032432,"uid":42364,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:44:13.000Z","msg":"用既人冇公德<br />\n整到鑲金都冇撚用啦"},{"pid":"98b8d034c06c7202b927b8240891a30e22409926","tid":1032432,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"繼撥款請社工又一德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1b3d5f6d56b450690002d5c2760676b025a1d1","tid":1032432,"uid":208973,"like":0,"dislike":2