br />\n所以比幾多億翻新 比呀伯同大陸人都係會亂咁痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5653ee9d98a74f71ad53b220f2dc6c4b767ecad1","tid":1032432,"uid":229609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T14:41:26.000Z","msg":"番新完個公廁可以考慮俾d大蝗搬入去住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1e2e5b03f56cd96d1dda47948b2d3f1e1e51b0","tid":1032432,"uid":181418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"其實保養都好重要，<br />\n翻新完無人打理好快殘"},{"pid":"86592b4cf14c0a09d362ad3f775ae7a9a1a799b4","tid":1032432,"uid":93615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"對公廁印象差除左佢舊之外仲係因為平時清潔保養好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c637632036bc3955f1408fc3df9daf2a260ed1","tid":1032432,"uid":65984,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:33:02.000Z","msg":"四腳獸或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c08d28162b4e198d046fb4abf1dff5c64a1dea","tid":1032432,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"低能， 翻新村民嘅公廁比佢地攞水用咋"}]}